sequenceDiagram
    participant App as bootstrap()
    participant BPM as BrowserPaneManager
    participant DC as DesktopControl
    participant SS as ServerSupervisor
    App->>BPM: new BrowserPaneManager(mainWindow, {0,0,0,0})
    App->>BPM: ensureSessionTab(session)
    App->>DC: new DesktopControl(paneManager)
    App->>DC: control.start()
    DC-->>App: {url, token}
    App->>SS: new ServerSupervisor({..., controlUrl, controlToken})
    App->>SS: supervisor.start()
    SS-->>App: {port, attached}
    Note over App: IPC: mc:browser:listTabs/openTab/closeTab/activateTab/navigate/setBounds<br/>IPC: mc:setZoomFactor
